          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="aWkcEURjoyIysUinpvPr-82" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 26px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Functional Requirements&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 26px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Search Functionality:&lt;/b&gt; The user must be able to discover events using filters such as the Event Title, the City/Location, and the specific Date of the show.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Event Information Display:&lt;/b&gt; The user must be able to view comprehensive details for a specific event, including the No of Seats (available vs. occupied), a detailed Description, and Metadata (cast, duration, language, ratings).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Booking Execution:&lt;/b&gt; The system must allow a user to select a seat and complete a transaction to Book a Ticket.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="400" x="100" y="880" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="aWkcEURjoyIysUinpvPr-83" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;Non Functional Requirements&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Target Scale:&lt;/b&gt; The system must be designed to support 100 Million Daily Active Users (DAU).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;High Availability:&lt;/b&gt; When users are searching or viewing an event, the system must prioritize being &quot;always online&quot; (High Availability). It is better to show slightly older data than to show an error page.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;High Consistency:&lt;/b&gt; When a user is booking a specific ticket, the system must be Highly Consistent. Two people should never be able to book the exact same seat at the exact same time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="470" x="100" y="1290" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
